comments: This version got heavy rotation at Radio Luxembourg. The pirate radio station had a show called "Smash Hits", where the DJs Barry Alldis and Don Moss occasionally smashed hit records that listeners grew tired of. The listeners had to give a good reason why they should smash the records, and got seven requests from Mandal in Norway. Prøysen, who quickly grew tired of the song himself, later mentioned this incident in another song, "Ei vise om ei vise".
